`]}),`
`,t.jsx(n.p,{children:'In regulated or operational domains, "I do not have evidence to answer that" is not a weak answer. It is a trust-preserving answer.'}),`
`,t.jsx(n.p,{children:"The retrieval layer should make unsupported claims hard to render, not merely discouraged by prompt text."}),`
