`,t.jsx(n.p,{children:"The eval should match the job."}),`
`,t.jsx(n.p,{children:"For a Q&A agent, citation correctness and retrieval recall matter more than eloquence. For a policy-generation agent, structured findings and traceable edits matter more than pretty prose. For an operational agent, safe failure behavior matters more than always having an answer."}),`
`,t.jsx(n.p,{children:'The best evals become a shared language with stakeholders. Instead of arguing whether the agent "seems better," you can say:'}),`
`,t.jsxs(n.ul,{children:[`
