`,t.jsx(n.p,{children:"The testing automation platform needed to orchestrate end-to-end test execution for Maverick compliance controls. A single test run could span multiple test suites and marketplaces. Each combination needed test data, an asynchronous test execution, result processing, and cleanup."}),`
