`,t.jsx(n.p,{children:"This avoids a polling loop. For a four-hour run with 60-second polling, one marketplace would require roughly 240 Lambda invocations and hundreds of state transitions. With three to five marketplaces running in parallel, polling cost and complexity multiply quickly. Callback keeps the orchestrator simple and lets DynamoDB remain the source of progress visibility."}),`
`,t.jsx(n.h2,{id:"failure-handling",children:t.jsx(n.a,{href:"#failure-handling",children:"Failure handling"})}),`
`,t.jsx(n.p,{children:"Every failure falls into one of three categories:"}),`
